{"tid":1162751,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"陣間約左佢出黎，準備同佢講清清楚，得就得唔得就放棄","createTime":"2019-05-20T04:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T07:46:08.000Z","uid":138138,"like":7,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fee1e2dfccad0060df0b70c80212ad4c6ef218f2","tid":1162751,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T04:56:55.000Z","msg":"追左佢咁耐，佢都係無咩表示<br />\n大佬阿，我都係一個普通人，我都係有我既耐性<br />\n其實直接同我講清講楚係咪唔得？？？？？？？<br />\n一直係度拖拖拖<br />\n次次諗住叫佢直接比個答覆我<br />\n又同我講未得住，下次先答你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你直接拒絕我，等我放棄，死左條心好過啦屌你老母<br />\n我當以前付出既時間，付出既金錢，付出既精神無左佢算<br />\n點解你要係咁拖，又頭畀個假希望我？？<br />\n你知唔知我真係會信我其實係仲有希望<br />\n其實仲有機會收得番我借左畀你既錢"},{"pid":"22236c61ac50168506a2e4858254a3882bb3a59f","tid":1162751,"uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:03:51.000Z","msg":"咁都有負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝你地以後都收唔到借左畀人個筆錢"},{"pid":"7e97ac520a43a780dfc19a81a3b214f6da15050a","tid":1162751,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:04:44.000Z","msg":"橙"},{"pid":"30b642787d1cf4be45ed112106f83666e94189bc","tid":1162751,"uid":220068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:07:26.000Z","msg":"咪傻啦 拒絕咗你仲邊有兵收"},{"pid":"403dfdbe39c570ffb1b1fc6f9f3cbdbff5ca37ee","tid":1162751,"uid":98041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:09:16.000Z","msg":"屌你數還數路還路啦 因為想追人而借錢比人 你係唔係無腦"},{"pid":"6a18fd33c303394907455da37c48e18c03bf3f87","tid":1162751,"uid":199641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:09:50.000Z","msg":"追左咁耐都冇下文自己心照啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係要衝出去柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd36c37280878b9d0af3c71143db680b7e1fa71","tid":1162751,"uid":138138,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"403dfdbe39c570ffb1b1fc6f9f3cbdbff5ca37ee","tid":1162751,"uid":98041,"like"